### CheckPoint — Admin Comments endpoints
### Requires an ADMIN account. See admin-users.http for the login request.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = PASTE_YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_HERE

### Delete a comment (moderation)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/comments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
